Hibana, there-- Whatever.

00:03:33.004 --> 00:03:34.714 position:50% align:center
Self-satisfied punk.

00:03:34.798 --> 00:03:36.299 position:50% align:center
[KISHIRI groans]

00:03:36.383 --> 00:03:38.677 position:50% align:center
[HIBANA] Gravel does not
