00:03:40.470 --> 00:03:42.263 position:50% align:center
Right, Shinra?

00:03:42.347 --> 00:03:43.431 position:50% align:center
Owie.

00:03:43.515 --> 00:03:46.017 position:50% align:center
[OBI] Uh... we do
appreciate you taking on

00:03:46.101 --> 00:03:48.687 position:50% align:center
a smaller company like ours.

00:03:51.106 --> 00:03:52.190 position:50% align:center
[HINAWA]
Enjoy.

00:03:52.273 --> 00:03:54.484 position:50% align:center
Yeah. Sure.

00:03:54.567 --> 00:03:55.819 position:50% align:center
[SPUTTER]
Sputter-sput.

00:03:55.902 --> 00:03:56.861 position:50% align:center
